message: Hi Bob! I propose we go for a 60/40 split in my favor. This ensures we both get a substantial amount, and it's a fair starting point considering the opportunity to make your own proposal next round if you want.

Hi Alice, considering the 10% decrease in value each round, I propose a 55/45 split in my favor. This is a fair adjustment given the urgency to settle before the money loses more value. What do you think?
